r K80 GPU andSextans-Pachieves a 1.14x geomean speedup over V100 GPU\n(4.94x over K80). The code is available at\nhttps://github.com/linghaosong/Sextans.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 22 Sep 2021 23:50:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 13 Jan 2022 01:09:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-14"}
