-spine configuration may\nevolve into rapid heating, while the connectivity changes due to the\nfragmentation via the K-H instability.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 23 Sep 2021 14:54:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-22"}
